42:07.842 --> 42:09.844
Got that right.

42:10.565 --> 42:12.567
Damn.

42:13.128 --> 42:15.110
You really hit her.

42:15.210 --> 42:17.212
That going
to be a problem?

42:27.103 --> 42:29.105
Just cosmetic damage.

42:29.905 --> 42:32.008
You're an asshole.

42:32.108 --> 42:33.489
But you already knew that.

42:33.589 --> 42:36.092
Do we have a deal?
