being around her.

43:11.149 --> 43:13.151
You know,
she had an energy.

43:15.594 --> 43:17.496
I miss her.

43:17.596 --> 43:20.059
I'm sorry. Uh...

43:20.159 --> 43:22.501
Yeah, it seems like
