43:55.636 --> 43:57.639
I'd start with two.

43:58.319 --> 44:00.321
Yeah. Thanks.

44:01.723 --> 44:03.425
So you think
that's her out there?

44:03.525 --> 44:05.067
I don't want
to think about it.

44:05.167 --> 44:06.348
Right. I mean, I--

44:06.448 --> 44:08.190
Me, I just,
I can't get over

44:08.290 --> 44:10.552
the coincidence,
you know, uh--

44:10.652 --> 44:12.114
Like, do you think that
maybe the same guy--

44:12.214 --> 44:14.216
What did I just say?

44:15.457 --> 44:17.460
I can't think
about it, you know.

44:19.302 --> 44:21.304
It's too hard.

44:22.505 --> 44:24.607
You know, this isn't
a cold case mystery

44:24.707 --> 44:27.190
for me or some bullshit.

44:31.795 --> 44:34.558
It never fucking goes away.

44:38.962 --> 44:40.965
Does it ever go away?

44:44.288 --> 44:46.470
I wish I'd...

44:46.570 --> 44:49.093
I'd have
protected her from...

44:50.054 --> 44:52.056
whatever I...

44:52.977 --> 44:54.979
I wish I'd have been
strong like that.

44:56.461 --> 44:59.084
Man, I-I'm sorry.

44:59.184 --> 45:04.530
I, I just started snapping
into this mode I have and...

45:04.630 --> 45:06.972
You know, it's, it's been
pretty messed up here,

45:07.072 --> 45:08.173
to tell you the truth.

45:08.273 --> 45:10.276
I generally live
in the sunshine.

45:10.676 --> 45:12.578
But this year,

45:12.678 --> 45:16.743
I mean, it has
eroded me, you know.

45:16.843 --> 45:19.846
It's just... Jesus, like...

45:23.129 --> 45:26.132
It's been pretty dark,
actually, you know.

45:27.334 --> 45:29.816
It's hard
to feel safe and, uh...

45:32.019 --> 45:34.021
Anyway.

45:34.581 --> 45:36.664
Look, I-I'm sorry. I...

45:41.389 --> 45:43.511
I'm not going to let
anything happen to you tonight.

45:45.793 --> 45:47.936
You believe me, right?

45:48.036 --> 45:50.058
Yeah.

45:50.158 --> 45:52.160
Yeah, I do.

45:54.803 --> 45:57.105
Tell you what, Jimmy,
end of the day,

45:57.205 --> 45:58.947
all I really want to do

45:59.047 --> 46:01.049
is get off
this shit mountain.

46:08.057 --> 46:10.059
Anaheim Shores...

46:25.355 --> 46:27.217
Proustian.

46:27.317 --> 46:29.440
You okay?
What the hell is in this?

46:33.284 --> 46:35.506
Oh, shit.
Oh, that's Trey's coconut rum.

46:35.606 --> 46:38.289
He fucking loves that shit.
Sorry about that. Hold up.

46:41.853 --> 46:44.696
You know, I, uh,
I think I'm just going to...

46:45.857 --> 46:47.078
ow, find Morty

46:47.178 --> 46:49.981
and, uh, get,
get out of here.

46:56.949 --> 46:58.951
Strong...

47:00.673 --> 47:02.675
ibuprofen.

47:55.691 --> 47:57.693
Au revoir, Morty.

48:12.829 --> 48:14.911
Oh, Jesus Christ.

48:26.684 --> 48:28.686
Ibuprofen, my ass.

48:35.413 --> 48:37.235
What happened to the girl?
Don't worry about it.
We're good.

48:37.335 --> 48:38.917
No, dude.
You look like shit.

48:39.017 --> 48:41.720
Yeah, because I was busy
fixing our problem.

48:41.820 --> 48:43.362
Saving you again.
You're welcome.

48:43.462 --> 48:44.843
Trey,
what did you do to her?

48:44.943 --> 48:46.525
It's not going
to be a problem

48:46.625 --> 48:47.887
for us anymore, okay.

48:47.987 --> 48:49.889
Oh, fuck, Morty,
I'm sorry.

48:49.989 --> 48:53.372
Oh, my God.
No one is going
to miss this girl.

48:53.472 --> 48:54.894
Okay? Nobody.
We all could have--

48:54.994 --> 48:57.977
Fuck you, guys.
Fuck you.

48:58.077 --> 48:59.419
You took this
way too far, man.

48:59.519 --> 49:01.501
I caught her trying
to steal my car.

49:01.601 --> 49:03.063
Okay?
Bullshit.

49:03.163 --> 49:04.744
She was gonna
go to the cops.

49:04.844 --> 49:06.626
I did what I had to do
to save your sorry ass.

49:06.726 --> 49:07.868
To save me?
Yeah.

49:07.968 --> 49:09.389
I didn't want
any of this.

49:09.489 --> 49:10.410
Yeah, well,
I didn't want to crash

49:10.410 --> 49:11.792
my 300K car

49:11.892 --> 49:13.934
because some chick's
going crazy on me again.

49:15.816 --> 49:17.198
That's the second time
you say that tonight.

49:17.298 --> 49:19.120
Say what?

49:19.220 --> 49:22.003
Some other chick
going crazy on you.

49:22.103 --> 49:25.126
Are you--
Are you talking about Chloe?

49:25.226 --> 49:27.208
Fucking shit.
Are you serious?

49:27.308 --> 49:29.531
We're gonna talk
about this right now?
Was it, Trey? Trey.

49:29.631 --> 49:31.012
Here we go.
What did you do?

49:31.112 --> 49:32.494
Hold on. Do you hear that?
Shit.

49:32.594 --> 49:34.176
No. Don't change the--
Shut the fuck up. Listen.

49:35.717 --> 49:37.719
Gotcha.

49:38.840 --> 49:40.843
Ah!

49:47.089 --> 49:48.471
Oh.
Oh, shit.

49:48.571 --> 49:50.032
I thought
you were asleep.

49:50.132 --> 49:52.475
Uh, well, you also thought
I was dead, right?

49:52.575 --> 49:54.317
So I guess this is
a thing I do now.

49:54.417 --> 49:55.799
You should have stayed down. Trey.

49:55.899 --> 49:57.440
Man, you fucking
ran me over.

49:57.540 --> 49:59.843
Chill out.
Look, whatever he told you,

49:59.943 --> 50:01.204
he is lying, okay.

50:01.304 --> 50:02.966
He killed Chloe... Okay.

50:03.066 --> 50:04.888
...and now he's doing it again.
We need to get her outside.

50:04.988 --> 50:06.690
He's just going
to leave you here to do
his dirty work,

50:06.790 --> 50:08.212
and then he's going to bail.

50:08.312 --> 50:09.934
Just leave you in this
haunted moose lodge,

50:10.034 --> 50:11.175
seeing Chloe
everywhere you look.

50:11.275 --> 50:12.817
Are you trying to play us

50:12.917 --> 50:14.578
against each other?

50:14.678 --> 50:16.180
We've been friends
for years.

50:16.280 --> 50:17.702
Bullshit. Okay.

50:17.802 --> 50:20.265
Jimmy, he killed her.
You understand?

50:20.365 --> 50:22.747
He killed Chloe.
Oh, my God, you bitch!

50:22.847 --> 50:24.549
This is pathetic, right?

50:24.649 --> 50:26.591
Trey, what did you mean?

50:26.691 --> 50:28.353
What?

50:28.453 --> 50:30.435
"Another chick going crazy
on you." What did you mean?

50:30.535 --> 50:32.718
Don't let her get inside
your head right now, man.

50:32.818 --> 50:34.480
It's just, Chloe.

50:34.580 --> 50:36.201
Chloe.

50:36.301 --> 50:37.603
Did she go crazy on you?

50:37.703 --> 50:40.846
Dude--
You said she had an accident.

50:40.946 --> 50:43.970
A bad reaction to the coke
I sold you, that she fell.

50:44.070 --> 50:45.772
That is what happened.
She fell.

50:45.872 --> 50:47.133
No, that is bullshit.

50:47.233 --> 50:49.375
Did you hit her?

50:49.475 --> 50:51.257
Did you push her?
No!

50:51.357 --> 50:52.339
Bullshit!

50:52.439 --> 50:53.420
Okay, none of this matters!

50:53.520 --> 50:54.581
We were kids.

50:54.681 --> 50:56.683
I mean, who cares?

50:59.206 --> 51:02.950
Jimmy, how long have
we known each other?

51:03.050 --> 51:04.471
Think about everything
we've been through.

51:04.571 --> 51:07.995
Man, you were always
like my big brother.

51:08.095 --> 51:12.360
You're my protector.
And now I can return the favour.

51:12.460 --> 51:14.842
You want out of all this?
I can get you out.

51:14.942 --> 51:16.945
Jimmy--

51:17.946 --> 51:19.447
Whatever you want.

51:19.547 --> 51:21.630
We just got to do
this one last thing.

51:24.553 --> 51:26.555
Jimmy, please.

51:28.477 --> 51:29.578
Alright.

51:29.678 --> 51:31.580
There he is.

51:31.680 --> 51:33.682
Let's get her outside.
It's cleaner that way.

51:47.097 --> 51:49.099
No.

51:50.180 --> 51:51.802
Okay. Come on.
Let's just get--

51:51.902 --> 51:53.904
Back up, man.

52:00.391 --> 52:02.393
Get out of my way.

52:03.554 --> 52:06.177
You ruined my life.
I ruined your life?

52:06.277 --> 52:08.259
I was the only good thing
you had going.

52:08.359 --> 52:11.262
You were a loser then,
just like you're a loser now.

52:11.362 --> 52:13.545
Look at you, still stuck
in this shithole?

52:13.645 --> 52:15.347
Let me tell you a secret.

52:15.447 --> 52:18.490
This is where you were
always going to be.

52:19.611 --> 52:21.033
Maybe.

52:21.133 --> 52:24.076
But at least I'm done
being your bitch.

52:29.702 --> 52:31.704
Oh!

55:22.565 --> 55:24.948
That is how
you fuckin' do it!

55:25.048 --> 55:26.029
Woo!

