Officer Buckley:
<i>Morning, Trey,</i>

55:29.092 --> 55:30.113
<i>It's your friendly neighbourhood</i>

55:30.213 --> 55:31.475
<i>parole officer.</i>

55:31.575 --> 55:32.516
Be right there.

55:42.186 --> 55:44.248
