Ah.

57:02.952 --> 57:04.013
<i>...responding to a tip</i>

57:04.113 --> 57:04.854
<i>from a parole officer...</i>

57:04.954 --> 57:06.656
Robocop.

57:06.756 --> 57:08.538
<i>...on the property
of the Deerfield Motel.</i>

57:08.638 --> 57:11.100
<i>Authorities have confirmed
