<i>whose body
and identification was found</i>

57:27.898 --> 57:29.960
<i>in a wrecked vehicle
near the property.</i>

57:30.060 --> 57:31.642
Mortimer?
<i>They're both believed</i>

57:31.742 --> 57:33.965
<i>to be victims
of a wealthy parolee,</i>

57:34.065 --> 57:34.966
<i>Trey Nelson.</i>

57:35.066 --> 57:36.127
<i>Stay tuned for more</i>

57:36.227 --> 57:38.289
<i>on this developing story.</i>

57:38.389 --> 57:39.971
<i>And now we turn
to county politics</i>

57:40.071 --> 57:42.534
<i>where a referendum
